ects exceeding 4,000sqm. Investigations are ongoing, with potential arrests expected.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/over-150-landowners-and-developers-face-cheating-charges-in-nashik-housing-fraud/129488606?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-77906/129488606.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}